# 🧠 MODULE PLAN: Custom Differential Evolution Optimizer (DEO)

## 0. Core idea (reminder to future self)

We implement **DE/best/1/bin**, where:

* Mutation uses best individual
* Trial vector uses binomial crossover
* Selection keeps best

Formula reminder (don’t rethink this later):

* Mutation:
  ( v = x_{best} + F \cdot (x_{r1} - x_{r2}) ) ([docs.scipy.org][1])
* Binomial crossover (CR) decides per dimension
* Replace if better

