# 8. Utilities

```python
def clip_to_bounds(x, bounds):
    return np.array([
        np.clip(x[i], bounds[i][0], bounds[i][1])
        for i in range(len(x))
    ])
```

```python
def random_vector(bounds):
    return np.array([
        np.random.uniform(low, high)
        for (low, high) in bounds
    ])
```

