# 9. Important implementation details (DON’T FORGET)

### Diversity issues

* Ensure `r1 != r2 != i`
* Ensure `best` is updated each generation

### Performance

* Cache fitness values (avoid recomputation)

### Seeds edge cases

* If seeds > pop → truncate
* If seeds empty → fallback to random

### Reproducibility

